<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Blog de Medicamentos – Farmacias Yair</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --navy:     #0a1628;
      --navy-mid: #112240;
      --blue:     #0057b8;
      --blue-lt:  #1a8cff;
      --teal:     #00b4cc;
      --green:    #3ec97a;
      --white:    #ffffff;
      --off:      #f2f5fb;
      --gray:     #dde3f0;
      --text:     #1a2340;
      --muted:    #5a6a8a;
      --pill-bg:  #e8f0fe;
      --pill-txt: #1a5eb8;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
      background: var(--off);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    header {
      background: var(--navy);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .logo-link { text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .logo-link img { height: 52px; width: auto; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); }
    .header-title {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-left: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      padding-left: 16px;
    }
    .header-nav { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .header-nav a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 7px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .header-nav a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--white); }
    .header-nav a.back {
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--white);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .header-nav a.back:hover { background: var(--blue-lt); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .blog-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0d2d5e 50%, #0a3d6e 100%);
      padding: 72px 32px 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .blog-hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(0,180,204,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(62,201,122,0.1) 0%, transparent 45%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 60% 90%, rgba(0,87,184,0.2) 0%, transparent 40%);
    }
    .cross-deco {
      position: absolute;
      right: 80px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 14rem;
      opacity: 0.04;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .hero-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(0,180,204,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,204,0.35);
      color: var(--teal);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero-inner h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.15;
      max-width: 650px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .hero-inner h1 em {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--teal);
    }
    .hero-inner p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 520px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 32px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .stat {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .stat strong {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--teal);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat span {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── SEARCH / FILTER BAR ── */
    .filter-bar {
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray);
      position: sticky;
      top: 80px;
      z-index: 100;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    }
    .filter-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .search-box {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: var(--off);
      border: 2px solid var(--gray);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 200px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .search-box:focus-within { border-color: var(--blue); }
    .search-box input {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--text);
      width: 100%;
    }
    .search-box input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }
    .filter-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .ftag {
      background: var(--pill-bg);
      color: var(--pill-txt);
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.18s;
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    }
    .ftag:hover { background: #d0e2ff; }
    .ftag.on { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--blue); }

    /* ── MAIN LAYOUT ── */
    .page-wrap {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 48px 32px 64px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    /* ── ARTICLE GRID ── */
    .articles-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .articles-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .articles-count {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Featured article */
    .article-featured {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
      min-height: 300px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.22s, box-shadow 0.22s;
    }
    .article-featured:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.13); }
    .af-visual {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628 0%, #0d3060 60%, #0057b8 100%);
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .af-visual::before {
      content: '💊';
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 10rem;
      opacity: 0.08;
      transform: rotate(-15deg);
    }
    .af-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      left: 18px;
      background: var(--teal);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .af-icon { font-size: 5rem; position: relative; z-index: 1; filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)); }
    .af-body { padding: 36px 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .af-body .meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .af-body .meta .dot { color: var(--gray); }
    .af-body h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.55rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .af-body p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; }
    .read-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 11px 24px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      width: fit-content;
      transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .read-btn:hover { background: var(--blue-lt); transform: translateX(3px); }

    /* Article grid */
    .articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .article-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .article-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }
    .ac-visual {
      height: 140px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .ac-tag {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 10px;
      left: 12px;
      background: rgba(10,22,40,0.6);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .ac-body {
      padding: 18px 20px 22px;
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .ac-meta {
      font-size: 0.73rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .ac-body h4 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
    .ac-body p {
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .ac-read {
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      width: fit-content;
      transition: gap 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .ac-read:hover { color: var(--teal); gap: 9px; }

    /* ── SIDEBAR ── */
    .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; }

    .sidebar-widget {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    }
    .widget-header {
      padding: 18px 22px 14px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--off);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .widget-header h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .widget-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }

    /* Newsletter widget */
    .newsletter-widget {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0d3060 100%);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px 22px;
      color: var(--white);
    }
    .newsletter-widget h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .newsletter-widget p { font-size: 0.84rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .nl-input {
      width: 100%;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 11px 16px;
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      outline: none;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .nl-btn {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--teal);
      color: var(--navy);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
      transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .nl-btn:hover { background: var(--green); transform: scale(1.02); }

    /* Popular posts */
    .pop-list { padding: 10px 0 6px; }
    .pop-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--off);
    }
    .pop-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .pop-item:hover { background: var(--off); }
    .pop-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gray);
      min-width: 28px;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .pop-info h5 {
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .pop-info span { font-size: 0.73rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* Tags cloud */
    .tags-cloud { padding: 16px 22px 20px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .tag-pill {
      background: var(--pill-bg);
      color: var(--pill-txt);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .tag-pill:hover { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); }

    /* ── ARTICLE MODAL (full article view) ── */
    .modal-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(10,22,40,0.75);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      z-index: 500;
      display: none;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 16px;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }
    .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
    .modal-box {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 24px;
      max-width: 760px;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      animation: slideUp 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      margin: auto;
    }
    @keyframes slideUp {
      from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to   { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .modal-hero {
      padding: 48px 48px 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), #0d3060);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .modal-hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(0,180,204,0.15), transparent 60%); }
    .modal-close {
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px; right: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: none;
      color: var(--white);
      width: 38px; height: 38px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: background 0.18s;
    }
    .modal-close:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }
    .modal-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(0,180,204,0.2);
      color: var(--teal);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,204,0.35);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .modal-hero h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.25;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .modal-meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      font-weight: 600;
      position: relative;
    }
    .modal-content {
      padding: 36px 48px 48px;
    }
    .modal-content p {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #3a4a6b;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .modal-content h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 28px 0 12px;
    }
    .modal-content ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .modal-content ul li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #3a4a6b;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }
    .callout {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f0ff, #d0e8ff);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
      border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--navy-mid);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      font-size: 0.83rem;
    }
    footer a { color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--white); }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .page-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .article-featured { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .af-visual { min-height: 200px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .articles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 20px; }
      .modal-hero { padding: 32px 24px 28px; }
      .modal-content { padding: 24px; }
      .modal-box { border-radius: 16px; }
    }

    /* ── LOAD ANIMATIONS ── */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease forwards;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .fade-in:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.12s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.19s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.26s; }
    .fade-in:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.33s; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<html lang="es">
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
     <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <header style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: transparent; border: none;">
        <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/garcia04brayan-hue/negocio/main/logo.png" 
            style="height: 60px;" alt="Logo">
       <span class="header-title" style="position: relative; top: -16px;">  Blog · Medicamentos</span>
  </header>
    <nav class="header-nav">
      <a href="#">Inicio Blog</a>
      <a href="#">Bebés</a>
      <a href="#">Dermocosméticos</a>
      <a href="https://farmaciasyair.com" class="back">← Volver a la tienda</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
</html>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="blog-hero">
  <div class="cross-deco">✚</div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-label">💊 Blog de Medicamentos</div>
    <h1>Tu guía de salud y <em>medicación responsable</em></h1>
    <p>Artículos redactados por farmacéuticos y profesionales de la salud para ayudarte a entender los medicamentos, usarlos correctamente y cuidar tu bienestar.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat"><strong>24</strong><span>Artículos</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>8</strong><span>Categorías</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>4</strong><span>Expertos</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FILTER BAR -->
<div class="filter-bar">
  <div class="filter-inner">
    <div class="search-box">
      <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#9baac8" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Buscar artículos…" oninput="filterArticles(this.value)"/>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-tags">
      <button class="ftag on" onclick="filterTag(this,'todos')">Todos</button>
